    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Curtains at the foot of a bed that could be drawn either in two directions, to cover the lower half of the sides and meet in the center of the end, or to cover the lower half of the sides only.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000001531/Cummings, Bed Hangings (1961)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cortinas a los pies de una cama que pueden ser extendidas en dos direcciones, para cubrir la parte inferior de los lados y encontrarse en el centro del fin, o para cubrir la parte inferior de los lados solamente.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bedgordijnen aan het voeteneinde en de zijkanten van het voeteneinde van een bed, soms alleen aan de zijkanten.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>位於床腳的床簾，可向兩個方向拉動，以遮蓋床鋪側邊的下半部並在床尾中間拉合，或是只遮蓋床鋪側邊的下半部。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
